transcript:
Customer: Hello.
Executive: Hello, good morning sir.
Customer: Ji, ji sir, sorry mat kehna chahiye mujhe.
IndiaMART se hai.
Executive: Haan ji sir.
Customer: Haan bolo.
Executive: Aapka call aaya tha, main janaab busy rahe the, toh main aapko.
Customer: Haan toh ab ye kab kitna time mein sahi ho jayega, mere ko bilkul conversion nahi mil rahi hai aur unhone kya baat kari thi kal aapne.
Executive: Sir aapki aawaz kat rahi hai mujhe, aap shayad bike pe ho toh main aapko thodi der mein connect karu kya sir?
Customer: Haan, theek hai.
Executive: Kitne time se connect karu sir?
summary:
Concerns:

- Customer is not getting any conversions.

- Wants to know when the issue will be resolved.



Resolution:

- Executive said the customer's voice was breaking.

- Executive offered to call back later.



Next Steps: 

- Executive will call back later.



Alert (If Any):

None

@@@Sentiment:

- Neutral -> Neutral



@@@Key Topics:

- conversions, technical issue, callback
